org.polarsys.chess.chessmlprofile.Dependability.DependableComponent

Interface AnalysisContextElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AnalysisContextElementImpl

    public interface AnalysisContextElement
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Analysis Context Element'. This stereotype is used to store the result of a V&V check.

    The following features are supported:

    • Type
    • Date
    • Conditions
    • Valid
    • Result
    • Root
    • Context Analysis
    • Base Component
    • Instantiated Architecture
    See Also:
    DependableComponentPackage.getAnalysisContextElement()
